# Database Rules

Database: PostgreSQL

Guidelines:

- Never duplicate shop data.
- Google place_id is the external unique identifier.
- Use timestamps on all tables.
- Prefer additive migrations.

Scoring Logic:

Recommendation score combines:
- distance
- rating
- review_count
- genre match
- diagnosis answers

AI must not redesign schema unless explicitly requested.
